## Summary

Implemented suite 18/P05 — Postgres + pgvector vector store:

- **`src/db/schema.ts`** — Drizzle schema for `chunks` (uuid PK, path, content_hash, chunk_index, text, heading, section, topics[], kind, date, cite_okay, voice_weight, embedding vector(1024), created_at) with `idx_chunks_path` btree and `idx_chunks_embedding` HNSW (vector_cosine_ops); plus `ingest_state` keyed by path.
- **`src/db/migrations/0000_perpetual_ender_wiggin.sql`** — generated by `drizzle-kit generate`, hand-augmented with `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector;` at the top.
- **`drizzle.config.ts`** — points at `src/db/schema.ts`, emits to `src/db/migrations/`, reads `POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING` (falling back to `POSTGRES_URL`).
- **`src/lib/llm/db.ts`** — lazy `postgres-js` client + Drizzle wrapper. Separate handles for runtime (`POSTGRES_URL`, pooled) and migrations (`POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING`, direct).
- **`src/lib/llm/store.ts`** — `upsertChunks`, `deleteChunksByPath`, `getIngestState`, `setIngestState`, `searchSimilar` (cosine via `<=>`, returns `similarity = 1 - distance`); filters: `kind` (string|array), `topics` (any-of via `&&`), `cite_okay` (default true).
- **`scripts/llm/migrate.ts`** — runs `CREATE EXTENSION` defensively then `migrate()` from `drizzle-orm/postgres-js/migrator`.
- **`package.json`** — adds `drizzle-orm`, `postgres`, `pgvector` (deps), `drizzle-kit` (dev dep); scripts `db:generate` and `db:migrate`.
- **`docs/v2_dep_decisions.md`** — documents Drizzle-vs-Prisma rationale, Postgres-js choice, pgvector deployment notes, and the Pinecone non-goal.
- **`.env.example`** — documents `POSTGRES_URL` / `POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING`.

